            <section id="how-it-works" class="container glass-effect">
                <h2 class="gradient-text">How It Works</h2>
                <div class="how-it-works">
                    <p>Getting started with AutoCode is simple:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Create a CLAUDE_KEY or GEMINI_KEY environment variable with your API key.</li>
                        <li>Navigate to your project folder in the terminal.</li>
                        <li>Run the following command:</li>
                    </ol>
                    <pre><code class="neon-glow">npx autocode-ai</code></pre>
                    <p>
                        AutoCode reads your README.md file and existing source code, interprets instructions using LLMs,
                        and generates the necessary project files and structure.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        For more details, see the
                        <a
